BASIC.name: Basic
BASIC.description: A nice petal, not too strong but not too weak.

LIGHT.name: Light
LIGHT.description: Weaker than most petals, but recharges quickly.

FASTER.name: Faster
FASTER.description: It's so light it makes your other petals spin faster

STINGER.name: Stinger
STINGER.description: It really hurts, but its very fragile.

ROCK.name: Rock
ROCK.description: Extremely durable, but takes a bit longer to recharge.

SPONGE.name: Sponge
SPONGE.description: Spreads damage over time. If the damage accumulated is greater than the period, you will take all remaining damage at once!

ANTENNAE.name: Antennae
ANTENNAE.description: Allows your flower to sense foes farther away. Does not stack.

ARMOR.name: Armor
ARMOR.description: Gives your flower a %-based resistance to damage. Does not stack.

THIRD_EYE.name: Third Eye
THIRD_EYE.description: Your petals orbit your flower at a further distance. Does not stack.

CACTUS.name: Cactus
CACTUS.description: Not very strong, but somehow increases your flower's maximum health.

LEAF.name: Leaf
LEAF.description: Gathers energy from the sun to heal your flower passively.

MISSILE.name: Missile
MISSILE.description: You can actually shoot this one.

MAGNET.name: Magnet
MAGNET.description: Your loot loves you even more!

PEARL.name: Pearl
PEARL.description: Say what now?? I can't hear you over the sound of my money!

SHELL.name: Shell
SHELL.description: Somehow gives you a working shield...

GRAPES.name: Grapes
GRAPES.description: It's a bundle of poisonous grapes!

SALT.name: Salt
SALT.description: It reflects damage back onto the enemy. Can stack with itself.

WALKINGSTICK_EGG.name: Walkingstick Egg
WALKINGSTICK_EGG.description: This one's a bit of a mystery...

PEAGUN.name: Peagun
PEAGUN.description: It's like diep kinda, but with peas!

PRIMROSE.name: Primrose
PRIMROSE.description: A weaker rose that loves your friends more than you do!

POWDER.name: Mysterious Powder
POWDER.description: Somehow makes your flower move faster! Does not stack with itself.
